snippet.title: Best VGM 1635 - Jade Cocoon - The Blue Cocoon Master ~ Koris
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2098 - https://youtu.be/eWsYdciDkqY

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS1
Jade Cocoon: Story of the Tamamayu (1998)
The Blue Cocoon Master ~ Koris
Kimitaka Mastumae
